data.meta_description: Time Magazine International Edition is the go-to news magazine for what's happening around the globe. You can rely on TIME's award winning journalists for analysis and insight into the latest developments in politics, business, health, science, society and entertainment.
data.text:
Read Time Magazine International Edition online

As a practical e-paper, Time Magazine International Edition now has even more to offer. Take your favourite magazine on your smartphone or tablet with you wherever you go. Time Magazine International Edition is now available with a YUMPU News subscription. But that´s not all! In addition to Time Magazine International Edition, countless other exciting online magazines and newspaper await. YUMPU News, the all-you-can-read subscription service - all magazines and newspaper are included in the price of £ 5.97 per month! Explore our many categories and we are sure you will find stories which will change your life. Enjoy the highest reading fun with our online magazines and newspapers. Thanks to the YUMPU News app, Time Magazine International Edition also accompanies you on your mobile devices with lots of exciting news, tasty recipes, tricky puzzles and the latest need-to-knows! No reception? No problem! Download your favourites to your personal kiosk and read the magazines offline in the best quality. YUMPU News offers fun for the whole family. To provide the highest reading experience for everyone, you can share your YUMPU News account with up to four other people. Read Time Magazine International Edition together or discover new magazines, just the way you like them. So that young and old can enjoy the huge variety of magazines and newspapers without a problem, many great extras ensure even more reading pleasure. Zoom in on all articles and pictures without quality loss, bookmark exciting articles for later and always find exactly what you want in countless issues using the search function. To make sure you always have the latest issue on hand, we will notify you as soon as a new issue from your favourite magazine or newspaper is published. Discover, read, share, inspire with your YUMPU News subscription. Start now with your 30 days for free!
